Controllers:-
	KeyBoard:-
		Start Game :
			Press P 
		Buckets Movement:
			Red:
				Left  : right_ctrl + left_ArrowKey
				Right : right_ctrl + right_Arrowkey
			Blue:
				Left  : right_alt + left_Arrowkey
				Right : right_alt + right_Arrowkey

		Cannon Movement : 
				Up          : s
				Down        : f
				rotate_up   : a
				rotate_down : d

		Laser :
			fire : space

		Screen :
			zoom_in   : up_ArrowKey
			zoom_out  : down_ArrowKey

		Bricks  :
			speed_up    : n
			speed_down  : m

		panning 
			move_right : right_ArrowKey
			move_left : left_ArrowKey

		Exit : esc


	Mouse :-
		Start Game :
			click left_button
		Buckets Movement :
			Drag and drop i.e. select the desired bucket and drop to the desired position (horizontal movement only)

		Cannon Movement  :
			Drag and drop i.e. select the desired cannon and drop to the desired position (vertical movement only)	
		
		Fire :
			click anywhere(except for the bucket region and cannon area) to fire at that position

		Zoom :
			Zoom_In  : scroll_up	
			Zoom_out : scroll_down

		panning :
			Hold RightButton and move


Scoring :-
	-  +10 points for hitting black brick
	-  +10 points for collecting red brick in the red bucket
	-  +10 points for collecting blue brick in the blue bucket
	-  +50 points for hitting golden brick (BONUS)
	-  -10 points for hitting blue/red brick
	-  -10 points for collecting bricks in wrong bucket

GameOver :-
    -  Collecting Black brick in any of the bucket

Bonus :-
	- Golden Brick for +50 points


